description: 1st Grade allows you to choose spelling, addition or subtraction by default it will randomly choose one question from each at a time. The skill will keep giving a question after another until you stop the game, you could say repeat to ask Alexa to repeat the question.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask first grade for addition.
Alexa, Ask first grade for subtraction.
name: First Grade Game
shortDescription: 1st Grade spelling, addition, subtraction skill game help kids specially 1st grader practice with the fun of playing a game with Alexa.
